JOHANNESBURG – Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF) Member of Parliament (MP), Mbuyiseni Ndlozi on Monday hosted eNCA’s 'As It Happens'. Affectionately known as The People’s Bae, Ndlozi again showed why he is more than just a handsome face. Other politicians that will make their appearance on the show later this week include the African National Congress’ Pule Mabe, the Democratic Alliance (DA)’s Natasha Mazzone, the United Democratic Movement (UDM)’s Bantu Holomisa and the Inkatha Freedom Party’s Lisa van Merwe. eNCA